{"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._550","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeMinHeightSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMinHeightSmall"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC18sizeMinHeightSmallSdvp","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"symbolKind":"property","title":"sizeMinHeightSmall","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeMinHeightSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeminheightsmall"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/sizeMinHeightSmall":{"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._550","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeminheightsmall","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeMinHeightSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"sizeMinHeightSmall","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMinHeightSmall","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"ic_t